name: DLIFE Home Interiors
description: DLIFE, the most reliable company of home interior designers in Mangalore has an excellent track record of 9000+ completed projects in South India. We welcome you to DLIFE showroom in Mangalore to navigate through the display of modular kitchen, bed rooms, living and dining room furnishing. Our consultants and designers offer the comfort and convenience of discussing requirements, different designs, material options and price estimates. We offer 100% customization of complete home interiors in Mangalore with modern style, maintaining durable quality in essence.
